{
  "stem": "2996.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'll first tell you something that I did, and then you will understand what-- what my answer is.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I felt that the average American knows far too little about his own country.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Knows far too little about the early days, the Founders, the Constitution, the Bill of Rights-- far too little.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh, they read somewhere something about Bill of Rights.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Who was Jefferson, who was Monroe and some of the other people?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And because of that, I did a daily radio program on KFWB at 8:00, from 8:00 to 8:30 in the evening, without any commercials.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the whole thing was called, For This We Fight.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And after the war was over, is For This We Fought.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And every night it was something different.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "United Nations, as you could see from some of this, was always under attack.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, United Nations was a communist device, according to them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Monday it was United Nations, the people's hope.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The second one was something about the Constitution.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "No, the second one was the Constitution-- yeah, the Bill of Rights and the Constitution.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "On Monday, we had different organizations-- primarily women's organizations-- come on for interviews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "This one is interested in health so it dealt with United Nations section on health.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "This is not the correct name for it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I forget it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "If it was labor, obviously the labor guys came on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So on Monday, always dealing with one United Nations facet, especially UNESCO.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they cannot come on the air unless every member of their organization-- let us assume it's the League of University Women-- every member of the League of University Women has to-- has to be reached.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Saying listen in on KFWB on such and such time, blah, blah, blah.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
